raper"><strong>21</strong>Oct</span></div></div></div><!-- .elementskit-entry-header END --><div class="elementskit-post-body ekit-highlight-border"><div class="post-meta-list"></div><h2 class="entry-title"> <a aria-disabled="true" data-card-link-removed="true"> Neumann Caps Off EURONASCAR Season with Rookie Trophy </a></h2><p>Victor Neumann concluded the NASCAR Whelen Euro Series season in triumphant fashion, clinching his second consecutive Rookie Trophy title. The young talent showcased remarkable consistency and skill throughout the year,&hellip;</p><div class="btn-wraper"> <a class="elementskit-btn whitespace--normal" id="" aria-disabled="true" data-card-link-removed="true"> Read More <i aria-hidden="true" class="icon icon-chevron-right"></i> </a></div></div><!-- .elementskit-post-body END --></div></div><div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6"><div class="elementskit-post-image-card"><div class="elementskit-entry-header"> <a aria-disabled="true" data-card-link-removed="true" class="elementskit-entry-thumb"> <img src="{{ asset('asset/insights/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/F3-Season2025.webp') }}" alt="AIX Racing Secures Three-Year FIA Formula 3 Deal"> </a><!-- .elementskit-entry-thumb END --><div class="elementskit-meta-lists elementskit-style-tag"><div class="elementskit-single-meta triangle_left"><span class="elementskit-meta-wraper"><strong>14</strong>Oct</span></div></div></div><!-- .elementskit-entry-header END --><div class="elementskit-post-body ekit-highlight-border"><div class="post-meta-list"></div><h2 class="entry-title"> <a aria-disabled="true" data-card-link-removed="true"> AIX Racing Secures Three-Year FIA Formula 3 Deal </a></h2><p>AIX Racing has secured its place in the FIA Formula 3 championship for the next three seasons, from 2025 to 2027. The team was among the ten selected from the&hellip;</p><div class="btn-wraper"> <a class="elementskit-btn whitespace--normal" id="" aria-disabled="true" data-card-link-removed="true"> Read More <i aria-hidden="true" cl